com.guardtime.envelope

Interface EnvelopeElement

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Annotation, AnnotationsManifest, Document, DocumentsManifest, Manifest, SingleAnnotationManifest, UnknownDocument
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmptyDocument, SignedDocument

    public interface EnvelopeElement
    Umbrella interface for any expected element of an Envelope. Contains generic methods that all components of an Envelope must implement.
